# ICA Website — Full Redesign: #78081C × #FFFF00 Next-Level Premium Theme

## Overview
Complete visual overhaul of the ICA Edu Skills website using the exact brand palette of **Crimson Red `#78081C`** and **Electric Yellow `#FFFF00`**. The current CSS already has these tokens partially defined but the design needs to be dramatically elevated with next-level animations, 3D effects, per-section unique fonts, responsive polish, and a truly stunning professional look.

---

## Color System

| Role | Value | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| Primary Background | `#78081C` | Page base, deep sections |
| Accent / Highlight | `#FFFF00` | Text, CTAs, active states |
| Dark Crimson | `#4A0511` | Cards, depth layers |
| Bright Crimson | `#9C0C24` | Hover states, gradients |
| Deep Black-Red | `#1A0008` | Darkest sections |
| Yellow-Gold | `#FFE500` | Button shadows, warm accents |
| Off-Yellow | `rgba(255,255,0,0.7)` | Subtitles, body text |

---

