---

## New Design Elements

### 🎨 Visual Upgrades
- **Hero**: Full-viewport crimson-to-black gradient bg with animated grain texture overlay, glowing crimson orbs, electric yellow particle constellation (updated colors)
- **Section Backgrounds**: Alternating between `#1A0008` (near-black) and `#4A0511` (deep crimson) for depth contrast
- **Cards**: Deep glassmorphism with crimson-tinted glass `rgba(120,8,28,0.6)` + yellow border glow on hover
- **Gradient Text**: Electric yellow → bright crimson → electric yellow shimmer

### 🚀 3D & Animation Upgrades
- **3D Tilt Cards**: All USP, Course, Journey, and Testimonial cards get `perspective(1000px)` 3D tilt on hover via JS
- **Magnetic Buttons**: `.btn-primary` gets magnetic pull effect (mouse tracking in JS)
- **Morphing Background Blobs**: Animated CSS `@keyframes` morphing SVG blobs behind Hero and CTA
- **Stats Ring Animation**: SVG stroke-dasharray animation when stats enter viewport
- **Scroll-Progress Bar**: Thin yellow line at top tracking scroll depth
- **Cursor Glow Trail**: Custom cursor with yellow glow halo
- **Section Entrance**: Staggered slide+fade with GSAP (already exists, enhance timing)
- **Button 3D Press Effect**: `translateZ` + box-shadow depth shift on `:active`

### 📱 Responsive Polish
- Fluid type with `clamp()` at every breakpoint
- Mobile-first stack: all grids collapse properly
- Touch-friendly button sizes (min 44px tap targets)
- Mobile menu: full crimson overlay with yellow links

### 🎬 Video
- Hero video stays (`https://res.cloudinary.com/...`) — properly positioned right-side on desktop, full-width centered below text on mobile
- `mix-blend-mode: screen` kept for seamless blend

---

## Proposed Changes

### styles.css — FULL REWRITE
#### [MODIFY] styles.css
- New root tokens (richer color palette with 8+ variables)
- 10 Google Fonts imported (Playfair Display, DM Sans, Space Grotesk, Raleway, Poppins, IBM Plex Mono, Bebas Neue, Lora, Syne, Inter, Outfit)
- Per-section font-family assignments
- 3D button effects with `transform-style: preserve-3d`
- Morphing blob animations
- Scroll progress bar styles
- Custom cursor styles
- Enhanced glassmorphism card styles
- All hover states with yellow glow shadows
- Full responsive media queries at 1200, 1024, 900, 768, 600, 480px

### index.html — TARGETED ENHANCEMENTS
#### [MODIFY] index.html
- Add scroll-progress bar `<div id="scrollProgress">` before navbar
- Add cursor glow `<div id="cursorGlow">` 
- Add morphing blobs `<div class="blob">` in Hero and CTA
- Font link updated to include all 10 families

### app.js — ENHANCEMENTS
#### [MODIFY] app.js
- Scroll-progress bar logic
- Custom cursor glow tracking
- Magnetic button effect
- 3D tilt on all cards (USP, Journey, Testimonial, Curriculum)
- Stats SVG ring animation
- Particle colors updated to match new palette

