## Verification Plan

### Browser Preview
- Open `index.html` in browser via subagent
- Verify color theme, fonts, animations, responsiveness
- Test mobile view at 375px width
- Verify video renders properly

### Visual Checks
- ✅ All text readable (yellow on dark red = high contrast ✓)
- ✅ All sections have distinct fonts
- ✅ Hover/3D effects work on cards
- ✅ Buttons have 3D press effect
- ✅ Particles use correct colors
